Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.71,0:17:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真乖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}什么都不知道真好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起
