Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全身抽搐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.29,0:17:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,脱发
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,体力下降
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经转移到肝脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.98,0:17:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,生存几率是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话非常的严峻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.47,0:17:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为已经是大人了…
