Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:57.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结果  我还是非常的无知
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常的无力
