Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.86,0:18:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.98,0:18:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凛  不要让我为难
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,林志
