Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.79,0:18:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:55.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:19:03.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,两个月后肿瘤恶化的数值都没有下降
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,林志
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想回家  想回家
