Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.99,0:19:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回到…我们的「那个」家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:36.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真可爱  折的真好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不去医院了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  永远都在凛的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自那以后  凛每天都折纸鹤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.52,0:20:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,坚信折到一千只秋姐的病就好的
