Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.51,0:20:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.02,0:20:41.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.65,0:20:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.08,0:21:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,秋姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.47,0:21:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,秋姐！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.13,0:21:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.23,0:21:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知为何…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看着夕阳就想回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.39,0:21:47.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无法饶恕任何伤害凛的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:52.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让任何人碰凛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.48,0:23:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深爱的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.37,0:23:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,燃烧吧  露营篝火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,燃烧吧  小凛与我的火热一夜
