Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.12,0:23:27.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有快燃尽你的生命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.49,0:23:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,青木大介
